creator: Devotionalappszone
descriptionHtml:
Class 12 Maths NCERT Solutions app is specially designed for the CBSE class 12 students to help them prepare for their exams. It also helps them throughout the year to complete their homework on time and double check the answers.


This app contains answers of all the chapters included in the CBSE Board class 12 NCERT book:

★ Chapter 1: Relations and Functions
★ Chapter 2: Inverse Trigonometric Functions
★ Chapter 3: Matrices
★ Chapter 4: Determinants
★ Chapter 5: Continuity and Differentiability
★ Chapter 6: Application of Derivatives
★ Chapter 7: Integrals
★ Chapter 8: Application of Integrals
★ Chapter 9: Differential Equations
★ Chapter 10: Vector Algebra
★ Chapter 11: Three Dimensional Geometry
★ Chapter 12: Linear Programming
★ Chapter 13: Probability


Main Features:

★ This app is in easy English Language.
★ Simple app. Works offline. No internet connection needed!
★ Professionally designed, user-friendly and intuitive interface.
★ Clear Font for better readability.
★ Easy to use.
★ Zooming Available
